We strive to provide you with the best possible Services. Accordingly, we may use the information we collect to provide, analyze, administer, enhance and personalize our services and marketing efforts, to create your Account, and to communicate with you, and to allow you to communicate with others, on these and other topics. By way of example, we may use your information to:
Determine your general geographic location, provide you with personalized news content, and quickly and efficiently respond to inquiries and requests;
Analyze your usage of the Services, and the way you interact with the Services, to help us understand our audience, improve the Services, and optimize the delivery of content to you;
Prevent, detect and investigate potentially prohibited or illegal activities, including the enforcement of our Terms;
Provide you with relevant advertising content, as required by certain Service Agreements (as such term is defined below) that we maintain with third parties; and
Communicate with you concerning the Services (for example, by email) so that we can send you news, details about new features of the Services, special offers and promotions, and to assist you with operational requests.
We use these technologies to help provided the Services to you and in order to save your profile and preferences for future visits or compile aggregate data about website traffic and interaction so that we can offer a better user experience and tools in the future. Further, these technologies also help us deliver ads for relevant products and services.
